{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3ed8163aa1","title":"关于联合政府式的联合学生会的论点","origin":"《右派言论选辑》（社会主义教育参考资料之一，内部材料　仅供参考，沈阳师范学院社会主义教育办公室 1958．3）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"503008f4a0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"3ed8163aa1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7eb95ac9a4","name":"沈阳师范学院"},{"id":"d6c7386ef7","name":"赵文英"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c44c81ff20","type":"title","text":"关于联合政府式的联合学生会的论点","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"e13a8b5a74","type":"authors","text":"沈阳师范学院赵文英","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"f71c39afe7","type":"subtitle","text":"(赵文英：沈阳师范学院外语系学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"0d8479bc96","type":"subtitle","text":"一、提出的理由：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"dc31f11b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)学生会是独立的组织，不应由党团员包办，应照顾到非党团员群众各民族。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"2fa2265060","type":"subtitle","text":"二、内容：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"fb577836b1","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)在组织成员上，为了符合目前社会力量对比，可规定党团员占60％的比例应照顾各民族。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"247aa44f6b","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)在组织机构上，把学术研究和事务工作并列，各占一半。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"822377a5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)在选举上，采取竞选方式。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"1e87731d3e","type":"subtitle","text":"三、解散过去学生会理由：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"774ced1f36","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)过去学生会选举不民主，等额选举民主基础不强，我要拟一个实际不存在的候选人名单，管保能选上。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"afda529a48","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)现在学生会陷入瘫痪状态，没有支持“鸣放。”付主席(右派)辞职，生活部长(左派)不称职。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"},{"id":"ec72af9db1","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)最活跃最积极的党团员在领导学术问题上毫无能为力。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1"}],"page":{"id":"88abfad63a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3ed8163aa1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}